"""Generate test ID with salient information

    Returns:
        str -- test ID
    """
crumbs = [('actual', actual_comp), ('places', places), ('abs_tol',
    format_tol(abs_tol)), ('rel_tol', format_tol(rel_tol))]
return ','.join([format_pair(crumb) for crumb in crumbs if crumb[1] is not
    None])
